# Test Fixtures

When working with anything under `tests/fixture/`, read
[Fixtures Structure](../docs/Architecture/FixturesStructure.md) first to
choose the correct sub-folder (`spec/`, `spec_extra/`, `edge_cases/`,
`edge_cases_extra/`).

When working with specification-related fixtures in `tests/fixture/spec/`
or `tests/fixture/spec_extra/`, also read
[Specification Cover Fixtures Structure](../docs/Feature/SpecificationCoverFixtures.md)
for the full directory layout, version-specific file mapping, and
modification rules.
